Rochester Eugene PRESLEY, petitioner,
v.
MISSISSIPPI.
No. 15-9008.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 13, 2016.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Mississippi dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
